      "text": "Meet Fifi the Fox and Milo the Mouse. One sunny day they decide to build a cozy den. But they know they need help, because the den is big!",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2Fa6e53cb2-9a95-4116-9c8a-3bbcc5530084_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775930898&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=PdvaCXNjj4n47KGBnJECGNh9syk%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "Fifi says, 'Let's work together!' Milo smiles and nods. Together they plan: Fifi will gather soft leaves, and Milo will find tiny stones for the den's floor.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2F95df1afd-b2d8-48ef-9f6a-c5686d6ae3a0_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775931001&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=pwNPi%2Fy0QVw%2B%2BPI%2B7oMfAy%2FfsQw%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "Fifi runs to the meadow. She finds fluffy moss and bright flowers. Milo hops through the grass. He finds smooth pebbles and shiny shells for the den.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2Fc36aa3f4-1522-4fde-8be9-a712bb6972be_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775931029&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=unxUZKctekyivzEwsftrqVuiwvQ%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "Back at the clearing, Fifi arranges the moss like a soft bed. Milo lines the edges with pebbles. Their paws work side by side, making the den safe and warm.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2Fde2a84c0-8ae5-4e4b-97bf-d45fbad23723_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775931131&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=QAIYqXJ8N25t0hGhWdMJ093Z3VQ%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "Soon the cozy den is ready! Fifi and Milo curl up inside. They feel proud, because they built it together. Teamwork made their dream come true.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2Ffeb13383-0397-45a1-a6c7-83f3849854bc_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775931162&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=Qb1GGlFyESN%2BqT5Y5zIFYXMgtqU%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
